Strategy_resp: I just wrote down what first popped into my head.
I thought about the pandemic and all the health workers and educators that helped people during dangerous times.
I was trying to remember the last time I was in a hotel and what I saw in the lobby while waiting to get my room card.
I was reaching deeply for some of these words. The letter 'f' is not one I use much.
I just thought back to some of my vocabulary tests in freshman English.
I was remembering all the sports that are just now beginning to be played again during the pandemic. I am concerned the players don't contract the virus.
I watch the animal channels with my children and enjoy their reactions to the animal's behavior.
It has been several months since I took the family out for lunch or dinner in a restaurant.
I thought of my own somewhat messy garage and some of the things I put in it.
